## Brightness keys

XF86MonBrightnessDown
	xbacklight -dec 15
XF86MonBrightnessUp
	xbacklight -inc 15

## Media keys
XF86AudioMute
	amixer sset Master toggle; pkill -RTMIN+10 blocks
XF86Audio{Raise,Lower}Volume
	amixer sset Master 5%{+,-}; pkill -RTMIN+10 blocks
XF86Audio{Next,Prev}
	mpc {next,prev}
XF86Audio{Pause,Play,Stop}
	mpc {pause,play,stop}
XF86Audio{Rewind,Forward}
	mpc seek {-,+}10
XF86Tools
	$TERMINAL -e ncmpcpp
